title: Newsom flying under the radar for MU
text:
Newsom flying under the radar for MU POSTED: 07:00 PM CDT Sep 30, 2015 UPDATED: 07:25 PM CDT Oct 01, 2015 
Linebacker Donavin Newsom is the 5th leading tackler on the MU football team with 18, but 8 of those came against Kentucky.
